                    <span class="sc-about-riccardo-chip">{{t "Founder & Managing Partner"}}</span>
                    <h2>Riccardo Curatolo</h2>
                    <p>Riccardo Curatolo is an economist and digital entrepreneur specializing in blockchain and cryptocurrencies. As founder and editor-in-chief of SpazioCrypto, he focuses on providing clear, verified, and education-driven insights into the economic and social impact of decentralized technologies.</p>

                    <div class="sc-about-riccardo-socials">
